# OBNESS FLOWERS - prototype website

This is a simple multi-page responsive website built with HTML, CSS, and JS. Orders are stored in browser `localStorage` (prototype). The admin page reads stored orders and allows marking delivered or deleting.

## How to run locally
1. Open the project folder in VS Code.
2. Use Live Server extension or open `index.html` in browser.
3. Add images to `assets/gallery/` named `img1.jpg`, `img2.jpg`, `img3.jpg` and put `logo.png` in `assets/`.

## Deploy
See instructions in the main documentation below to deploy on GitHub Pages, Netlify, or Vercel.

## Production features (optional)
- Real SMS via Twilio (requires serverless function)
- Real geocoding / maps via Google Maps API (requires API key)
